{"tid":1801214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【支那人就是反人類】塞班島全國遊行聲援港人爭取自由民主    4支那蝗涉襲擊塞班人被捕","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T13:45:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a68962610243285809b76b05d8b0551beb40d4f","tid":1801214,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"人類人權就係追求自由民主<br />\n支那蝗係動武唔准其他人有自由民主<br />\n支那蝗本身就係反人類<br />\n<br />\n=================================<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9e2iALTFij9GkJM1CoScyA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/2e426baf2b38bfb67cf788364953a123\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9e2iALTFij9GkJM1CoScyA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F2e426baf2b38bfb67cf788364953a123&h=a3c4b4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國太平洋屬地塞班島周日（22日）有民眾遊行，聲援香港反修例運動，期間有人不滿示威者阻擋去路，雙方先口角後動武。警方接報到場，拘捕4名涉嫌打人的遊行人士，另有2名不滿遊行的民眾受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n事發周日傍晚6時3分，一批人在塞班島加拉班地區遊行，他們手持標語牌表達訴求。目擊者稱，一人走上前要求示威者讓路，遭一批男示威者以標語牌襲擊，導致左眼下方骨折；另一人上前試圖阻止襲擊時，亦遭同一批人打傷。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有指該批示威者是當地華僑，他們遭當地的親中團體挑釁，當遊行至一間中國人開設的海鮮餐館時，兩批人互相指罵，之後有人先發難襲擊示威者。"},{"pid":"8a1ba4cb2b44de9016ec01989a014c5684ad54b4","tid":1801214,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdf9dcc670952d5d706bcdba1dc9c3a67e68848","tid":1801214,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"點撚樣表達感謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb11637a58806c5c22e276b57e6d19c